{"tid":2078642,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"物理治療赴英國攻讀 回流執業無難度","createTime":"2020-06-25T07:59:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T10:08:06.000Z","uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eef4c93f8f0a24868e40bb89ecca0634f7918a95","tid":2078642,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://jupas.mingpao.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/ges-06242020-a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjupas.mingpao.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F06%2Fges-06242020-a.jpg&h=7581dbad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.beagazine.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/beaAbanner-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.beagazine.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FbeaAbanner-1.jpg&h=fba193a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n物理治療及言語治療未來人手需求殷切，不少DSE考生都希望入大學修讀，但偏偏在香港這兩個課程的學額少，而且收生要求亦高，競爭非常激烈。環城海外升學中心總監繆敏鶯（Heidi）表示，每年有不少未能在港入讀上述學科的考生會轉到英國升學，學額較多之餘，畢業後回港執業亦無困難。<br />\n<br />\n理工大學的物理治療學科(JS3636)每年取錄150人，去年收生分數平均為DSE最佳六科34.4分，考生每科都要考獲5至5*級才有機會獲取錄，否則只可望門輕嘆，但繆女士表示，在英國只需DSE最佳三科554級便有資格報讀，當中必須包括生物科。<br />\n<br />\n在英國讀物理治療，基本上只要取得合格成績畢業，以及完成一千個小時實習，便可向英國健康及護理專業協會註冊成為英國物理治療師，回港後亦可向物理治療師管理委員會取得認證。"},{"pid":"826b53b989d6f82481cb19c5abd21ca24cace880","tid":2078642,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:01:16.000Z","msg":"$"},{"pid":"0f37a7e406200583840c596b69ae24192e99597c","tid":2078642,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"有錢就有得讀"},{"pid":"a818fd6f10d5ccda51497c6c9e16457589ec6edd","tid":2078642,"uid":139611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:06:24.000Z","msg":"遵理藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffcc81a6f43c97b34eac8425dacae85cfb970b1","tid":2078642,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T10:08:06.000Z","msg":"多左人行呢條路"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0f37a7e406200583840c596b69ae24192e99597c","tid":2078642,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T08:47:06.000Z","msg":"有錢就有得讀"}}